{"tid":1913652,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"細哨朗拿顛奴使用假護照無罪釋放，巴拉圭警察居然搶著合影","createTime":"2020-03-07T03:34:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-08T04:23:38.000Z","uid":25345,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"025dc11f1c2f03da7c2235518c34e6bd17c58938","tid":1913652,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T03:34:53.000Z","msg":"昨日，前世界足球先生、巴薩功勛球員，因為在巴拉圭使用假護照，被巴拉圭警方逮捕，這一消息是震驚了世界足壇。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據悉，朗拿顛奴此次前往巴拉圭，是為了參加一項幫助兒童的公益計劃，同時也為了介紹自己的新書。但在入境時，朗拿顛奴因為使用了假的巴拉圭護照而被逮捕。從朗拿顛奴被曝光的假護照來看，朗拿顛奴使用了真實姓名、生日和照片，但卻把國籍由巴西改為巴拉圭。作為世界足壇的巨星，朗拿顛奴的國籍眾所周知，他使用假護照處境，確實是心夠大的。<br />\n<img src=\"http://dingyue.ws.126.net/2020/0306/b8a94a72j00q6r3mz000yc000fa00bhm.jpg?imageView&amp;thumbnail=750x0&amp;quality=85&amp;type=jpg&amp;interlace=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2020%2F0306%2Fb8a94a72j00q6r3mz000yc000fa00bhm.jpg%3FimageView%26thumbnail%3D750x0%26quality%3D85%26type%3Djpg%26interlace%3D1&h=e4e045ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過今日從巴拉圭傳來了好消息，雖然朗拿顛奴因為使用假護照被逮捕，但是經過長達8個小時的審訊後，目前這位巴西巨星已經被無罪釋放，他也沒有被巴拉圭警方起訴，朗拿顛奴現在是行動自由，可以隨時離開巴拉圭。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://dingyue.ws.126.net/2020/0306/3e148754j00q6r3mz000rc000f800cvm.jpg?imageView&amp;thumbnail=750x0&amp;quality=85&amp;type=jpg&amp;interlace=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2020%2F0306%2F3e148754j00q6r3mz000rc000f800cvm.jpg%3FimageView%26thumbnail%3D750x0%26quality%3D85%26type%3Djpg%26interlace%3D1&h=70783171&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n使用假護照，還能無罪釋放，不得不說巨星就是巨星。而根據巴拉圭當地媒體的報道來看，朗拿顛奴被巴拉圭警方逮捕後，雖然名義上是接受了長達8個小時的審訊，但實際上則是成為一場另類的球星見面會。朗拿顛奴剛被逮捕後，當地警察就要求與他合影，甚至在朗拿顛奴被送到警局後，負責審訊的警官還向朗拿顛奴要求合影，並把照片發到了社交網絡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://dingyue.ws.126.net/2020/0306/2cb3a174j00q6r3mz000yc000gs009gm.jpg?imageView&amp;thumbnail=750x0&amp;quality=85&amp;type=jpg&amp;interlace=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2020%2F0306%2F2cb3a174j00q6r3mz000yc000gs009gm.jpg%3FimageView%26thumbnail%3D750x0%26quality%3D85%26type%3Djpg%26interlace%3D1&h=52163ecd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n看來朗拿顛奴即便退役多年，但他的人氣依舊居高不下，至少在整個南美洲，這位前世界足球先生，所到之處總能引起大量的關注。這不在剛使用完假護照後，朗拿顛奴還能微笑的從警局走了出來，並把審訊變成了球迷見面會，真是不得不佩服朗拿顛奴的影響力！"},{"pid":"61e1a4d71fe14093671dfc12b3ed05bf735d3fdf","tid":1913652,"uid":173852,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T03:35:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁出名用假護照做乜"},{"pid":"648da096e702ea43df6ed4b364952e794927bf54","tid":1913652,"uid":25345,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T03:40:16.000Z","msg":"法律面前"},{"pid":"19645326f20ebe664e980498486e4c145eeda9a2","tid":1913652,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"61e1a4d71fe14093671dfc12b3ed05bf735d3fdf","tid":1913652,"uid":173852,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T03:35:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁出名用假護照做乜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T03:40:33.000Z","msg":"屌慣靚女，有時都想試下豬扒嘅"},{"pid":"bad8cf13cffe6cea23d99c13c89cf8f2cd2b4ed8","tid":1913652,"uid":53672,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T03:41:17.000Z","msg":"當時用假護照比人斷正時 佢有無話自己唔係細哨"},{"pid":"25e2971803fbf72653a66989c55d7237096bef60","tid":1913652,"uid":205462,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T03:42:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KPdgKQp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKPdgKQp.jpg&h=af2da38b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"46df9c7b4968df89dce12b54c35357c279b4b2ff","tid":1913652,"uid":52881,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T03:43:57.000Z","msg":"估到個結果係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ee5629f48eab5fc1b481e231226b3e4ce52ea60","tid":1913652,"uid":33730,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"61e1a4d71fe14093671dfc12b3ed05bf735d3fdf","tid":1913652,"uid":173852,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T03:35:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁出名用假護照做乜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T03:45:21.000Z","msg":"佢之前無交罰款, 真嗰本巴西護照俾政府取消咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8282ee08c6c275dc87713d67e62ef22dedb45117","tid":1913652,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46df9c7b4968df89dce12b54c35357c279b4b2ff","tid":1913652,"uid":52881,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T03:43:57.000Z","msg":"估到個結果係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T03:45:45.000Z","msg":"用假護照都走得甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3a6ebb57fb4c7c7390be4f8b861fb886d72da9a","tid":1913652,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T01:42:39.000Z","msg":"巴西退役球星朗拿甸奴（Ronaldinho）涉嫌使用假護照案件，他和兄長羅拔圖（Roberto Assis）3月7日現身巴拉圭法院應訊。雖然他們希望可以獲釋，但法官認為他們有潛逃風險，因此下令當局繼續收押兩人。<br />\n<br />\n冇放喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09fbe1a047d2726039cb12d2594fff6503f5e1a2","tid":1913652,"uid":81270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b3a6ebb57fb4c7c7390be4f8b861fb886d72da9a","tid":1913652,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T01:42:39.000Z","msg":"巴西退役球星朗拿甸奴（Ronaldinho）涉嫌使用假護照案件，他和兄長羅拔圖（Roberto Assis）3月7日現身巴拉圭法院應訊。雖然他們希望可以獲釋，但法官認為他們有潛逃風險，因此下令當局繼續收押兩人。<br />\n<br />\n冇放喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T01:44:59.000Z","msg":"個邊唔係法庭話事的，基本上警察話放就放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a396702882c811c2bdb1328c6df4847ba8876ef1","tid":1913652,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"09fbe1a047d2726039cb12d2594fff6503f5e1a2","tid":1913652,"uid":81270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b3a6ebb57fb4c7c7390be4f8b861fb886d72da9a","tid":1913652,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T01:42:39.000Z","msg":"巴西退役球星朗拿甸奴（Ronaldinho）涉嫌使用假護照案件，他和兄長羅拔圖（Roberto Assis）3月7日現身巴拉圭法院應訊。雖然他們希望可以獲釋，但法官認為他們有潛逃風險，因此下令當局繼續收押兩人。<br />\n<br />\n冇放喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T01:44:59.000Z","msg":"個邊唔係法庭話事的，基本上警察話放就放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T01:46:45.000Z","msg":"但宜家係坐緊"},{"pid":"2b22f87c410d03cb5155685e1f3dec8c3364a3d3","tid":1913652,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T01:47:35.000Z","msg":"他們7日到首都亞松森（Asuncion）最高法院應訊，稱願意留在酒店軟禁，並以羅拔圖患有心臟病為由，希望避過牢獄之災。不過法官魯伊斯（Clara Ruiz Diaz）指兩人涉嫌所犯的罪行嚴重違反巴拉圭的利益，認為他們有潛逃風險，所以下令兩人須繼續在監獄扣押，根據巴拉圭法例，當局有6個月時間完成調查。<br />\n<br />\n朗拿甸奴的律師圖馬（Tarek Tuma）在庭外表示，他（朗拿甸奴）根本不知道發生甚麼事，又形容判決令人難以置信，因此會表明上訴。<br />\n<br />\n有警官向傳媒透露，朗拿甸奴和羅拔圖與其他疑犯扣留於同一間囚室，當局為他們提供肥皂、坐墊和驅蚊用品等，並強調朗拿甸奴不會因為他的身份而獲特別對待。"},{"pid":"cb061ab8f0d22825761edcba4a5390815902b2b3","tid":1913652,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b22f87c410d03cb5155685e1f3dec8c3364a3d3","tid":1913652,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T01:47:35.000Z","msg":"他們7日到首都亞松森（Asuncion）最高法院應訊，稱願意留在酒店軟禁，並以羅拔圖患有心臟病為由，希望避過牢獄之災。不過法官魯伊斯（Clara Ruiz Diaz）指兩人涉嫌所犯的罪行嚴重違反巴拉圭的利益，認為他們有潛逃風險，所以下令兩人須繼續在監獄扣押，根據巴拉圭法例，當局有6個月時間完成調查。<br />\n<br />\n朗拿甸奴的律師圖馬（Tarek Tuma）在庭外表示，他（朗拿甸奴）根本不知道發生甚麼事，又形容判決令人難以置信，因此會表明上訴。<br />\n<br />\n有警官向傳媒透露，朗拿甸奴和羅拔圖與其他疑犯扣留於同一間囚室，當局為他們提供肥皂、坐墊和驅蚊用品等，並強調朗拿甸奴不會因為他的身份而獲特別對待。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T01:53:14.000Z","msg":"佢根本想留巴拉圭"},{"pid":"f88e17629b07504b31944c9e5eb6911f9358e2ae","tid":1913652,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T02:08:09.000Z","msg":"好黑暗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cac46d6ab84bda60f69836bb36ea3d2a8ac5141","tid":1913652,"uid":11081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T02:40:42.000Z","msg":"護照係真，國藉錯左姐"},{"pid":"522affbdab49138f8d7e7729d14e2486065d1bdc","tid":1913652,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T02:46:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rxn5LRE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRxn5LRE.jpg&h=522d0e1e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d726d8e94e71b6f87471baa675cbdc1a42c6f6c6","tid":1913652,"uid":149607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T03:24:18.000Z","msg":"8個鐘捉住佢黎輪流影相"},{"pid":"9159b39aef0c0a8ade6a2428929126efb936c475","tid":1913652,"uid":261505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T04:23:38.000Z","msg":"咁有錢都唔用英美護照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}